Package sjc.parser

Provides for StaticJava parser and lexer.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StaticJavaV4Listener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by StaticJavaV4Parser.
    StaticJavaV4Visitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by StaticJavaV4Parser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ParserUtil
    This class provides a helper method to call the StaticJava ANTLR v4 parser.
    StaticJavaV4BaseListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of StaticJavaV4Listener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
    StaticJavaV4BaseVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of StaticJavaV4Visitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
